headline: ICE First Look at Mortgage Performance: Serious delinquencies hit 17-month high while foreclosure activity remains historically muted
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, November 21, 2024--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE:ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, reports the following "first look" at October 2024 month-end mortgage performance statistics derived from its loan-level database representing the majority of the national mortgage market.
